<div class="tool-panel guide-panel">
  <div class="section-heading">
    <h2>怎么选参数</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="guide-grid">
    <div>
      <strong>Sample Rate</strong>
      <p>填 SigmaStudio 项目的采样率。48 kHz 时 1 sample = 0.020833 ms。</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <strong>延迟时间 / Samples / 距离</strong>
      <p>修改任一项即可反推其它项。SigmaStudio 里通常抄整数 samples。</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <strong>声速</strong>
      <p>默认 343 m/s。需要按现场温度校正时，勾选气温修正。</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <strong>Cur / Max</strong>
      <p>Cur 是四舍五入后的整数 samples，Actual Cur delay 是实际可实现延迟。</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="tool-panel preset-panel">
  <div class="section-heading">
    <h2>场景预设</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="preset-row" aria-label="Delay 参数预设">
    <button type="button" data-delay-preset="one-ms">1 ms</button>
    <button type="button" data-delay-preset="one-meter">1 m 距离</button>
    <button type="button" data-delay-preset="one-sample">1 sample</button>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="split-fields three">
  <div class="tool-panel compact-panel">
    <label class="field-label" for="sample-rate-input">Sample Rate (Hz)</label>
    <input id="sample-rate-input" inputmode="decimal" value="48000" />
  </div>

  <div class="tool-panel compact-panel">
    <label class="field-label" for="sound-speed-input">声速 (m/s)</label>
    <input id="sound-speed-input" inputmode="decimal" value="343" readonly />
  </div>

  <div class="tool-panel compact-panel">
    <label class="toggle-field">
      <input id="temperature-mode-input" type="checkbox" />
      <span>按气温修正声速</span>
    </label>
    <label class="field-label" for="temperature-input">气温 (°C)</label>
    <input id="temperature-input" inputmode="decimal" value="20" disabled />
  </div>
</div>

<div class="split-fields three">
  <div class="tool-panel compact-panel">
    <label class="field-label" for="delay-ms-input">延迟时间 (ms)</label>
    <input id="delay-ms-input" inputmode="decimal" value="1" />
  </div>

  <div class="tool-panel compact-panel">
    <label class="field-label" for="samples-input">Samples</label>
    <input id="samples-input" inputmode="decimal" value="48" />
  </div>

  <div class="tool-panel compact-panel">
    <label class="field-label" for="distance-input">距离</label>
    <div class="inline-field">
      <input id="distance-input" inputmode="decimal" value="0.343" />
      <select id="distance-unit">
        <option value="m">m</option>
        <option value="cm">cm</option>
        <option value="ft">ft</option>
        <option value="in">in</option>
      </select>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="status-line" data-status data-state="ok">
  <span aria-hidden="true">●</span>
  <span>等待处理</span>
</div>

<div class="tool-panel result-panel">
  <div class="section-heading">
    <h2>结果抄写表</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="result-grid">
    <div class="result-row">
      <span>SigmaStudio Cur</span>
      <strong data-delay-result="cur-samples">-</strong>
      <em>写入 Delay 的整数 samples</em>
    </div>
    <div class="result-row">
      <span>Actual Delay</span>
      <strong data-delay-result="actual-delay">-</strong>
      <em>整数 samples 对应的实际延迟</em>
    </div>
    <div class="result-row">
      <span>Distance</span>
      <strong data-delay-result="distance">-</strong>
      <em>当前声速下的声学距离</em>
    </div>
    <div class="result-row">
      <span>1 Sample</span>
      <strong data-delay-result="one-sample">-</strong>
      <em>当前采样率下的单 sample 时间</em>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="tool-panel">
  <label class="field-label" for="delay-output">输出</label>
  <textarea id="delay-output" readonly spellcheck="false" placeholder="换算结果会显示在这里"></textarea>
</div>
